      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not even about resting anymore. i mean i have rested, i've taken breaks, i've tried to change my surroundings... nothing works. the loop is just part of who i am at this point. no matter what i do, i just wake up tomorrow and it's the same shit all over again. it feels like there's no version of the future where this actually stops.",
